<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">raṅganātham samyagvayyām</hi><note n="303-2">Read <hi rend="grantha">ºgvaryyām</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha">saparyyām punarakṛta <unclear>ya</unclear>śōdarppaṇō gōppaṇā ryyaḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> viśvēśam raṅgarājam vṛṣabhagiritaṭāt gō</hi><note n="303-3">Read <hi rend="grantha">ºtaṭādgō</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>pa</unclear>ṇaḥ (<g type="danda">.</g>) kṣō <unclear>ṇi</unclear>dēvō nītvā svām rājadhā nī nnijabalanihatōtsiktatauluṣkasainyaḥ [<g type="danda">.</g>] kṛtvā</hi>
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>śrī</unclear>raṅga<unclear>bhū</unclear>mim</hi><note n="303-4">Read <hi rend="grantha">ºbhūmim</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>kṛta</unclear>yuga <unclear>sahitānta</unclear>ntulakṣmīmahībhyām samsthāpyām sarōjōtbhava</hi><note n="303-5">Read <hi rend="grantha">ºjōdbhava</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha">Iva kurutē sādhu ca<unclear>ryy</unclear>ām saparyyām <g type="ddanda">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied></hi>
</p>

